# Build Believe Fit — React frontend environment
# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in. Vite only exposes vars prefixed VITE_.
#
# The anon/publishable key is safe in the client bundle — RLS is the real
# boundary, and privileged admin reads go through the token-gated
# bbf-admin-roster edge function, not the anon key.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://ihclbceghxpuawymlvgi.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# NOTE — Command Center admin tokens are NOT build-time vars. Never bundle a shared
# secret (CLAUDE.md §7). The roster (BBF_COACH_AGENT_TOKEN) and Comlink
# (BBF_ADMIN_TOKEN) gates are hydrated at RUNTIME by src/lib/adminAuth.js, in order:
#   1. window.BBF_COACH_AGENT_TOKEN / window.BBF_ADMIN_TOKEN  (a non-committed
#      env.js injected at deploy, mirroring the legacy monolith) — zero-friction.
#   2. typed once into the Command Center unlock gate → cached in sessionStorage
#      for the tab session only (never localStorage, never the bundle).
